    "description": "Tool for finding haplotypes in sequence data. Each individual is \"painted\" as a combination of all other sequences. It can output a range of features, including: Sample haplotypes, Expectation of the number of recombination events, and a range of related features. It can be used to generate PCA from dense data, for creating data summaries for fine STRUCTURE, and for dating admixture events.",
